Python Package Updates
-----------------------

Requirements
-------------

sudo apt-get install python3-setuptools   |  Bunlardan emin değilim.  
sudo apt-get install python3-distutils    |  Ama yüklemekte zarar yok.
sudo apt-get install python3-pip
sudo apt-get install python3.6-dev
sudo apt-get install python3.7-dev
sudo apt install libgirepository1.0-dev
sudo apt-get install libpq-dev python-dev libxml2-dev libxslt1-dev libldap2-dev libsasl2-dev libffi-dev libcups2-dev libcairo2-dev

Packages
---------

